  "description": "This individual presents the compact, orderly build associated with deskbound work and long hours under lamplight. Brown eyes set beneath straight brows track details with habitual precision, while brunette hair kept in a plain arrangement frames an oval face marked by faint ink-stains along the cuticles. Light skin shows the even pallor of an indoor occupation, and the mouth holds a firm line shaped by constant recitation of terms and figures. The hands remain notably steady and fine-boned, formed for seals, ledgers, and the handling of bond papers.",
